# UI / UX Standards — Phase UI-X (2026)

Premium enterprise election platform. Mobile-first. Fully responsive.

## Visual rules

- Flat professional colours only — **no gradients**
- Civic navy primary (`brand-*`, `#1E3A6E`) — institutional, election-appropriate
- Plenty of whitespace; 12px card radius; 10px input radius; soft shadows only
- Inter Variable, weights 400–700 only
- Cards must not feel crowded

## Colour tokens (Tailwind)

| Role | Token / Hex |
|------|-------------|
| Primary | `brand-*` / `#1E3A6E` |
| Primary hover | `brand-hover` / `#152E55` |
| Secondary | `slate-700` / `#334155` |
| Background | `surface-muted` / `#F5F7F9` |
| Surface | `surface` / `#FFFFFF` |
| Border | `border` / `#E2E8F0` |
| Success | `success-*` / `#2E7D32` |
| Warning | `warning-*` / `#CA8A04` |
| Danger | `danger-*` / `#C62828` |
| Information | `info-*` / `#0F766E` |

## Status badge colours

| Status | Variant |
|--------|---------|
| Draft | grey |
| Scheduled | blue-grey |
| Open | green |
| Paused | amber |
| Closed | red |
| Archived | dark grey |

## Spacing tokens

- Page padding: `px-page` (32px)
- Section spacing: `space-y-section` (32px)
- Card padding: `p-card` (24px)
- Input/button gap: 16px

## Authentication

- **Single unified sign-in page** — no role selector
- **Student / candidate (default):** index number only → OTP (`Enter your index number`, placeholder e.g. `BC/ITS/24/047`)
- **Staff:** subtle **Staff access** link → email or username → password → OTP
- OTP screen must not expose role labels

## Required page states

Every page: **loading** (skeleton), **empty**, **error**

## Components — reuse before creating

`AppShell`, `PageHeader`, `SectionHeader`, `VCard`, `VButton`, `VInput`, `VTable`, `StatCard`, `EmptyState`, `LoadingSkeleton`, `StatusBadge`, `VIcon`

## Responsive

- Sidebar: 280px expanded / 88px collapsed; drawer on mobile
- Tables: card layout on mobile
- Lazy-load Vue route pages

## Accessibility

Keyboard navigation, visible focus rings, ARIA labels, 44px touch targets, WCAG AA contrast.
